  "purpose": "Conformance fixture for anchoring an AgentGraph static-analysis SCAN event as an EvidenceAnchor. action_ref is the correlation key, derived from the intent tuple {agent_id, action_type, scope, timestamp} per action-ref-v1 \u2014 NOT from the verdict. The verdict (grade/findings/cve_list/outcome) is a separate field, so the correlation key stays stable across re-scans of the same target while the evidence it points at can change. action_type encodes the scanner operation (static_analysis.scan); scope is the target tool identity (MCP server URI / package ref). A verifier confirms identity (the anchor) and evidence (the verdict) independently, with no access to AgentGraph infrastructure.",
